1. *Majore* su se pokazali veoma uspešnim u ovom trenutku. (The majors have proven to be very successful at this moment.)
2. On je izabran za *majore* u vojsci. (He was chosen to be a major in the army.)
3. *Majore* su često pozvani da prezentuju na raznim skupovima. (Majors are often invited to present at various gatherings.)
4. Ona je pre dve godine postala *majore*. (She became a major two years ago.)
5. *Majore* su učili o osnovnim principima vojne strategije. (The majors were learning basic principles of military strategy.)